========================
ESP32-CAM Board Overview:
=========================

    Microcontroller: ESP32-D0WD (dual-core 32-bit LX6 microprocessor)
    Camera Module: OV2640 (2MP) with support for OV7670 (without the built-in flash)
    Operating Voltage: 5V (regulated to 3.3V on board)
    Wi-Fi: 802.11 b/g/n
    Bluetooth: BLE and Bluetooth Classic
    Flash Memory: 4MB (or 8MB in some variants)
    MicroSD Slot: Supports up to 4GB
    UART, SPI, I2C, PWM, ADC, DAC support

ðŸ’¡ Built-in LEDs

    White LED (Flash LED):
        Controlled by GPIO 4
        Used as a flashlight or illumination source for the camera.

    Red LED (Status LED):
        Controlled by GPIO 33
        Turns on during power-up or can be programmed as an indicator.
